room_title: Escape room "Dracula's Castle" by Mystery Escape Room Tucson in Tucson
room_description: It was thought that Abraham Van Helsing vanquished the evil that resided in the ancient castle but after discovering that the monster inside lived, he promptly returned to this nightmarish place!  That was the last anyone ever saw of him.  It is up to you now to put a stop to the evil that lurks inside.  Be swift and take caution for when the clock strikes midnight, the monster awakes!
